#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn17.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 17 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 17 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga "
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 13–20. Suvaṇṇanikkhasuttādiaṭṭhaka → suvaṇṇanikkha-janapadakalyāṇī (pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:0.3"
msgid "13–20. Suvaṇṇanikkhasuttādiaṭṭhaka "
msgstr "13–20. A Gold Coin, Etc. "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli2.234, sc1
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.2"
msgid "“Idhāhaṃ, bhikkhave, ekaccaṃ puggalaṃ evaṃ cetasā ceto paricca pajānāmi: "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when I’ve comprehended the mind of a certain person, I understand: "

msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.3"
msgid "‘na cāyamāyasmā suvaṇṇanikkhassāpi hetu … pe … "
msgstr "‘This venerable would not tell a deliberate lie even for the sake of a gold coin.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.4"
msgid "suvaṇṇanikkhasatassāpi hetu … "
msgstr "‘… for the sake of a hundred gold coins.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.5"
msgid "siṅgīnikkhassāpi hetu … "
msgstr "‘… for the sake of a gold doubloon.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.6"
msgid "siṅgīnikkhasatassāpi hetu … "
msgstr "‘… for the sake of a hundred gold doubloons.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.7"
msgid "pathaviyāpi jātarūpaparipūrāya hetu … "
msgstr "‘… for the sake of the whole earth full of gold.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.8"
msgid "āmisakiñcikkhahetupi … "
msgstr "‘… for any kind of material reward.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.9"
msgid "jīvitahetupi … "
msgstr "‘… for the sake of life.’ … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.10"
msgid "janapadakalyāṇiyāpi hetu sampajānamusā bhāseyyā’ti. "
msgstr "‘… for the sake of the finest lady in the land.’ "

msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.11"
msgid "Tamenaṃ passāmi aparena samayena lābhasakkārasilokena abhibhūtaṃ pariyādiṇṇacittaṃ sampajānamusā bhāsantaṃ. "
msgstr "But some time later I see them tell a deliberate lie because their mind is overcome and overwhelmed by possessions, honor, and popularity. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.12"
msgid "Evaṃ dāruṇo kho, bhikkhave, lābhasakkārasiloko … pe … "
msgstr "So brutal are possessions, honor, and popularity. …” "

msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.13"
msgid "evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.14"
msgid "Dasamaṃ. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:1.15"
msgid "Dutiyo vaggo. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:2.1"
msgid "Dve pāti dve suvaṇṇā ca, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:2.2"
msgid "Siṅgīhi apare duve; "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:2.3"
msgid "Pathavī kiñcikkhajīvitaṃ, "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn17.13-20:2.4"
msgid "Janapadakalyāṇiyā dasāti. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></blockquote></article></section></body></html>
